  "2290520": {
    "name": "Sneaky Pirates",
    "steam_appid": 2290520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Sneaky Pirates 中扬帆起航！一款激动人心的在线多人社交推理游戏，在开放的海洋中，欺骗、策略和快速的动作相碰撞！在这场智力较量中，最多 4 名玩家伪装自己，混入舰队中，偷偷摸摸地寻找并从对手身上偷取宝藏——这一切都要在不被发现的情况下进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/29d94fb5d073368c5b65263a5fca08a9.avif?t=1750285283\" width=616 height=126 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偷取胜利 – 比赛结束时，拥有最多黄金的海盗为至尊。如果平局，最先偷到的人将赢得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/f3044951518184a5c0bd3b51ceeb3261.avif?t=1750285283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras_big/f3044951518184a5c0bd3b51ceeb3261.avif?t=1750285283 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在人群中隐藏 – 融入由 AI 控制的船只海洋中，精心策划下一步的行动，同时保持隐身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/a53777e5e5825072f1867e1235a23512.avif?t=1750285283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras_big/a53777e5e5825072f1867e1235a23512.avif?t=1750285283 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化或反击 – 使用特殊能力逃脱困境，甩掉追击者，或击败其他海盗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/e77f9276d4fb501c96fded2a2085c2d9.avif?t=1750285283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras_big/e77f9276d4fb501c96fded2a2085c2d9.avif?t=1750285283 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制你的船只 – 购买并装备外观升级，让你的船只独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/0490cf0db065f325f451b488098eb945.avif?t=1750285283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras_big/0490cf0db065f325f451b488098eb945.avif?t=1750285283 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的游戏风格 – 保持隐藏，稳妥行事，或者放开一切冒险去偷窃——两种方式都能带来胜利！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有赢家是安全的 – 海洋的潮汐随时变化——一个巧妙的最后一秒偷窃可以改变一切！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >早期访问中不断进化 – 冒险才刚刚开始！我们期待着通过社区反馈，扩展 Sneaky Pirates，增加新内容和新功能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能欺骗、偷窃并智胜其他海盗吗？加入我们，证明你是七大海上最狡猾的海盗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras/ca6b99c3c8393cfe34a8690638d7f353.avif?t=1750285283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290520/extras_big/ca6b99c3c8393cfe34a8690638d7f353.avif?t=1750285283 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
